# Slim the build context for Railway's Docker build.
# Without this, Docker uploads several GB of node_modules to the daemon.

# Workspaces · resolved fresh inside the image
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.next/
**/build/
**/.expo/

# VCS
.git/
.github/

# Local secrets — never bake into image
**/.env
**/.env.*
.env.local
.env.example
**/.envrc

# Mobile app build artifacts — not part of the api-server image
artifacts/xico-mobile/.expo/
artifacts/xico-mobile/web-build/
artifacts/xico-mobile/ios/build/
artifacts/xico-mobile/android/build/

# Editor + OS noise
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs + tmp
**/*.log
**/tmp/
**/.cache/
**/coverage/

# Test scratch
**/__tests__/*.snap
test-pg.mjs

# Plan artifacts (vault is outside the repo anyway)
.superpowers/
.claude/
docs/superpowers/

# Documentation that doesn't ship in the runtime image
*.md
!artifacts/api-server/README.md
HANDOFF_*.md
FINAL_HANDOFF.md
INTEGRATIONS_AND_ENV.md
AGENTS.md

# Large archives accidentally in tree
ai-context-export.zip
